{"tid":861446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高雄佛心早餐！果醬吐司7元 港幣都覺平","createTime":"2018-10-14T06:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T07:09:58.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3b1a93711942afd0cf70ea24b17d8b374e30b419","tid":861446,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"物價飆漲的時代，網友卻發現有家「佛心早餐店」，果醬吐司最便宜的竟才賣7元，整家店最貴的是漢堡加蛋25元，大家都直呼不可思議！<br />\n一名網友在臉書「爆廢公社二館」社團上傳照片，地點在高雄一家早餐店，牆上價目表列出各品項，草莓吐司7元，其他果醬吐司10元；火腿吐司10元，加蛋加5元。蘿蔔糕一片10元，蔥油餅15元，整張價目表看下來，最貴的品項為漢堡加蛋25元。<br />\n<br />\n網友看了驚呼：「好便宜！」、「20年前的價格？」、「這怎麼賺錢啊」、「佛心早餐」、「擺明就是欠我買」、「我國小時候的物價&hellip;大概20～25年前了」、「明明就是其他早餐店賣太貴...不過人家也是要賺錢哈哈」。<br />\n也有許多網友跪求地址，「高雄哪裡」、「地址報出來！！！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181014/1444524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181014%2F1444524&d=m6G9QNRFau2K256fxrbYNE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=b11a32ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181014%2F1444524&h=c15f60d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181014/1444524</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181014/640_a7f2e5ef8590ef5dc74d3551f9a6b39f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181014%2F640_a7f2e5ef8590ef5dc74d3551f9a6b39f.jpg&h=5a37a625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南台灣是我退休首選"},{"pid":"a340d60c50561c3240d52be494ce5233ea81a6b7","tid":861446,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e46ecd4ba1345b7aa619f88de3bd64aca5b0c9e","tid":861446,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a340d60c50561c3240d52be494ce5233ea81a6b7","tid":861446,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"ci